* Dinobot growled and looked down at Tavatron, he knew very well that they 
were to be inside of the Ark but he couldn't stand it in there! To many bots 
running around, he liked to be in places that a bot could move around 
without having to swerve around other bots.
Dinobot looked longingly at the doors again but then sighed, there was no 
use in fighting it...orders were orders.
He looked towards Tavatron and snarled...*

"I was..."

* Dinobot shook his head, he was about to say 'trying to get away' but 
thought that he had better not. He sighed and looked longingly at the doors 
again, what he'd give to at least get out for a mega-cycle or two. Then the 
idea hit him, there were rooms in the base itself that other bots didn't go 
much, he looked down at Tavatron again.

" Do you know a place where I can get some peace? It is far to crowded here 
for my liking."

* Dinobot wasn't sure if Tavatron would want to join him, she looked so 
ready to spring into action.*
